  "prompt": "How do I add more than one WordPress site in Godaddy's Deluxe hosting plan?",
  "response": "GoDaddy's Deluxe Linux Hosting plan allows you to host **multiple WordPress sites** on a single account. Here\u2019s how you can add more than one WordPress site:\n\n---\n\n### **Steps to Add Multiple WordPress Sites on GoDaddy Deluxe Hosting**\n\n1. **Confirm Your Plan Allows Multiple Sites**:\n   - The Deluxe Linux Hosting plan supports hosting **one primary domain and one additional domain** (or more, depending on the plan). Ensure your plan supports the number of sites you want to host.\n\n2. **Access Your GoDaddy Account**:\n   - Log in to your GoDaddy account and navigate to your **Hosting Dashboard**.\n\n3. **Add a New Domain**:\n   - In your hosting dashboard, go to **Websites > Manage**.\n   - Click **Add Website** or **Add Domain**.\n   - Follow the prompts to add a new domain or subdomain.\n\n4. **Install WordPress for the New Site**:\n   - After adding the domain, go to **Websites > Manage**.\n   - Select the new domain and click **Set Up**.\n   - Choose **WordPress** from the list of applications and follow the installation wizard.\n\n5. **Manage Your Sites**:\n   - You can switch between your sites in the hosting dashboard under **Websites > Manage**.\n   - Each site will have its own WordPress admin dashboard.\n\n---\n\n### **Using cPanel to Add Multiple Sites (if applicable)**:\nIf your GoDaddy hosting plan includes cPanel:\n1. Log in to **cPanel** from your hosting dashboard.\n2. Use the **Addon Domains** feature to add additional domains.\n3. Install WordPress for each domain using the **Softaculous Apps Installer** (available in cPanel).\n\n---\n\n### **Important Notes**:\n- **Storage and Bandwidth**: Ensure your plan has enough storage and bandwidth for multiple sites.\n- **Performance**: Hosting multiple sites on one plan may affect performance. Consider upgrading to a higher-tier plan if needed.\n- **Backups**: Keep regular backups of each site to avoid data loss.\n\n---\n\nBy following these steps, you can host and manage multiple WordPress sites on GoDaddy\u2019s Deluxe Hosting plan.",
